<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Web Server Response</title>
<style>
body {
font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
background-color: #f4f7f6;
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
align-items: center;
height: 100vh;
margin: 0;
text-align: center;
}
.container {
padding: 40px 60px;
background: #ffffff;
border-radius: 12px;
box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}
h1 {
color: #2c3e50;
font-size: 2.5em;
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
p {
color: #34495e;
font-size: 1.2em;
border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
padding-top: 20px;
}
.node-id {
color: #e74c3c;
font-weight: bold;
font-size: 1.5em;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<h1>Welcome to the Web Application!</h1>
<p>This request was successfully served by:</p>
<p class="node-id">{{ ansible_hostname | upper }}</p>
<p>HAProxy is correctly routing traffic.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
